{"tid":2095544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"洞庭湖水位持續上升　新華社：防汛形勢嚴峻","createTime":"2020-07-05T14:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T02:26:40.000Z","uid":39464,"like":95,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"2df05d64e89cbb8c750645ad76c48bc48d856972","tid":2095544,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:04:05.000Z","msg":"洞庭湖水位持續上升，《新華社》報道，防汛形勢嚴峻。<br />\n<br />\n洞庭湖區共有29個堤垸、858公里堤防的水位超出警戒，環洞庭湖地區正在組織人員巡堤查險，準備搶險物資。<br />\n<br />\n內地中央氣象台表示，預計未來四天，持續性強降雨將影響西南地區東部至長江中下游一帶。<br />\n<br />\n貴州、重慶、湖北、江西、安徽、浙江等多個省市，預計累計降雨量將有100至300毫米，湖北東部、安徽西南部局部超過400毫米，預料湖南西北部等地區有大暴雨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535932-20200705.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535932-20200705.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj34E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=339f88e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535932-20200705.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=89b735b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535932-20200705.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a634ea4b5494d13f12482d798c02eba537191eca","tid":2095544,"uid":24788,"like":110,"dislike":1,"score":109,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"洞庭湖草頭鄉"},{"pid":"8b1769cc4498990961b9f67efc04393ac3d3298f","tid":2095544,"uid":75815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:09:17.000Z","msg":"上陽村"},{"pid":"07b28daa1030d96dd00e0d9d94b93cc1c6ebfd2b","tid":2095544,"uid":6132,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:15:42.000Z","msg":"之前成日話洞庭湖乾涸，而家咪滿足你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669cc579953ca2de5f53a7eab1efe0efe9cc168d","tid":2095544,"uid":2218,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"中国歲月靜好....這是假新聞黑